DRAFT Draft SP 800-90 Series: Random Bit Generators=20
800-90 A Rev. 1: Recommendation for Random Number Generation Using Determin=
istic Random Bit Generators=20
800-90 B: Recommendation for the Entropy Sources Used for Random Bit Genera=
tion=20
800-90 C: Recommendation for Random Bit Generator (RBG) Constructions

In light of recent reports, NIST is reopening the public comment period for=
 Special Publication 800-90A and draft Special Publications 800-90B and 800=
-90C.
NIST is interested in public review and comment to ensure that the recommen=
dations are accurate and provide the strongest cryptographic recommendation=
s possible.
The public comments will close on November 6, 2013. Comments should be sent=
 to RBG_Comments@nist.gov.=20
=20
