 Security Bulletin titled "NIST Opens Draft Special Publication 800-90A, Re=
commendation for Random Number Generation Using Deterministic Random Bit Ge=
nerators, For Review and Comment (Supplemental ITL Bulletin for September 2=
013)" to support the draft revision effort.

